column2: Thank you Santiago for this great weekend at the #SantiagoEPrix. It was not exactly what we expected but we are more than ready for next stop: Mexico here we come !  #ABBFormulaE
Thank you Santiago for this great weekend at the #SantiagoEPrix. It was not exactly what we expected but we are more than ready for next stop: Mexico here we come !  #ABBFormulaE
